Baik.

245
00:21:29,914 --> 00:21:33,626
HAN SEOL-AH
YOON SEUNG-JAE, CHOI YOUNG-HO, LEE SU-HO

246
00:21:36,838 --> 00:21:39,716
Aku yakin mereka ingin melindungi
wanita yang terluka ini.

247
00:21:39,799 --> 00:21:42,635
Pria cenderung terbutakan

248
00:21:42,719 --> 00:21:43,720
saat jatuh cinta.

249
00:21:45,096 --> 00:21:47,807
Mereka serahkan segalanya kepadanya,
bahkan nyawa mereka.

250
00:21:48,599 --> 00:21:51,644
HAN SEOL-AH

251
00:21:55,314 --> 00:21:56,774
Kalau begitu, katakan.

252
00:21:58,192 --> 00:22:00,236
Siapa pria berikutnya
yang akan jatuh hati…

253
00:22:01,946 --> 00:22:02,864
kepada Han Seol-ah?

254
00:22:08,536 --> 00:22:11,956
YOON SEUNG-JAE, CHOI YOUNG-HO, LEE SU-HO

255
00:22:14,459 --> 00:22:15,293
Lee Su-ho.

256
00:22:15,376 --> 00:22:16,544
Choi Young-ho.

257
00:22:18,796 --> 00:22:19,672
Yoon Seung-jae.

258
00:22:20,757 --> 00:22:23,217
Apa yang kau peroleh dari kematian mereka?

259
00:22:24,218 --> 00:22:25,636
Satu, dua kali itu kebetulan.

260
00:22:26,512 --> 00:22:28,973
Tapi jika sampai tiga kali,
itu bukan kebetulan.

261
00:23:13,768 --> 00:23:20,775
SIREN

262
00:23:25,571 --> 00:23:26,656
Lee Su-ho.

263
00:23:26,739 --> 00:23:27,615
Choi Young-ho.

264
00:23:28,157 --> 00:23:29,075
Yoon Seung-jae.

265
00:23:31,410 --> 00:23:34,789
Mereka pernah menjalin hubungan
dengan wanita yang sama sebelum tewas?

266
00:23:36,582 --> 00:23:39,877
Nn. Kim Yun-ji pasti meminta nomormu
untuk memberitahumu tentang ini.

267
00:23:41,212 --> 00:23:42,547
Tunggu sebentar.

268
00:23:42,630 --> 00:23:44,882
Kenapa bawa kasus asuransi jiwa
ke asuransi umum?

269
00:23:44,966 --> 00:23:45,800
Ke tim penjualan.

270
00:23:47,969 --> 00:23:50,263
Bisa buatkan kartu nama untukku
di asuransi umum?

271
00:23:50,763 --> 00:23:51,681
Kartu nama?

272
00:24:10,116 --> 00:24:10,992
1 PESAN BELUM DIBACA

273
00:24:11,492 --> 00:24:12,577
Ini kantor manajemen.

274
