276
00:24:23,087 --> 00:24:24,380
Selamat pagi.

277
00:24:24,463 --> 00:24:25,882
Kau datang lebih awal, Nn. Han.

278
00:24:25,965 --> 00:24:27,216
Sang-mi.

279
00:24:28,176 --> 00:24:30,344
Jasa kurir apa yang biasa kita gunakan?

280
00:24:30,428 --> 00:24:32,430
Dallyeo Quick. Kau perlu mengirim sesuatu?

281
00:24:34,849 --> 00:24:36,350
Boleh minta nomor teleponnya?

282
00:24:42,273 --> 00:24:43,441
Seol-ah.

283
00:24:44,317 --> 00:24:46,360
Kau yang kirim anggur itu ke aku?

284
00:24:50,239 --> 00:24:51,699
Kalau memang mau dirahasiakan,

285
00:24:51,782 --> 00:24:53,951
