KANTOR POLISI GANGHA

623
00:53:00,219 --> 00:53:02,054
-Apakah dia informannya?
-Ya.

624
00:53:06,392 --> 00:53:07,560
Do Eun-hye.

625
00:53:08,144 --> 00:53:09,562
Dia mahasiswa pascasarjana

626
00:53:09,645 --> 00:53:11,772
yang sedang bermagang di Royal Auction.

627
00:53:19,572 --> 00:53:20,823
Nn. Do Eun-hye.

628
00:53:21,407 --> 00:53:24,869
Identitasmu dan semua ucapanmu di sini
akan dijaga kerahasiaannya.

629
00:53:29,832 --> 00:53:31,000
